Home>Business Heads>Vikas Parihar

Vikas Parihar




Managing Director, OgilvyOne Africa
Vikas is the Managing Director,OgilvyOne Africa,based in Nairobi. He is an Integrated Marketing Communication and Digital Marketing Professional with more than 10 years of experience across the
industry.  His expertise spans a whole range of Integrated Marketing Services including devising plans for improving business performance,product promotion,overall organizational growth and enhancing brand image. 
In the short time he has been around,Vikas has headed the digital teams of global advertising companies like Havas Worldwide and TBWA for countrywide operations,and also directed various inter-agency functions such as Strategy and Planning,and Business Development.
Industries of expertise: Consumer Durables and electronics, FMCG, Technology,Healthcare,Travel and Hospitality,Social Development and Ecommerce.



10+yrs
 experience



















