Company Overview of WPP Scangroup Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
WPP Scangroup Limited provides integrated marketing communication services worldwide. It offers advertising, media investment management, advertising research, public relations, digital advertising, and communications marketing strategies for product and services. The company was formerly known as Scangroup Limited and changed its name to WPP Scangroup Limited in June 2015. WPP Scangroup Limited was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Nairobi, Kenya.


The Chancery5th FloorValley RoadUpper Hill, PO Box 34537Nairobi,  00100KenyaFounded in 1999



Phone: 254 20 2710021

Fax: 254 20 2718772

www.wpp-scangroup.com







