WPP Scangroup Limited Key Developments

WPP Scangroup Limited Proposes Amendments to its Articles of Association
May 1 17
WPP Scangroup Limited proposed amendments to its articles of association of the company, for approval at the AGM to be held on May 26, 2017.


WPP Scangroup Limited, Annual General Meeting, May 26, 2017
May 1 17
WPP Scangroup Limited, Annual General Meeting, May 26, 2017, at 08:00 Coordinated Universal Time. Location: Bomas of Kenya, Lang’ata Road Nairobi Kenya Agenda: To consider financial stamen for the year ended December 31, 2016; to consider first and final dividend; to elect directors; to approve remuneration of directors; to consider amendments of articles of association; and to consider other special business.


WPP Scangroup Limited Appoints Robert N'gan'ga as New Creative Head
Feb 1 17
WPP-Scangroup has appointed Robert N'gan'ga as the new creative head. N'gan'ga has a broad range of agency and client side experience from Redhouse Group, Scanad and RedSky, where he headed creative departments in the respective agencies. N'gan'ga brings over 15 years of experience to the role.  In his most recent assignments, he has been the creative mind behind the iconic campaigns for Tusker, Tusker Lite and Google. In his new role, he will oversee the creative team, and will be responsible for creative output.


